high_descs: Turn away from tub and towards the container on the floor with toilet paper in it.
Pick up roll of toilet paper from container on the floor.
Place toilet paper on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move toilet paper from container to back of toilet.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk up to the bin that is sitting on the right side of the toilet.
Pick up the roll of toilet paper from the bin.
Walk towards the toilet that is to the left of the bin.
Place the toilet paper on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move a roll of toilet paper to the toilet.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the toilet.
Take the toilet paper out of the bin.
Turn around to see the toilet.
Put the toilet paper on top of the toilet water tank.
anns.task_desc: Put the toilet paper on the toilet.
